```plantuml
@startuml gregoryjohnsonjg6_angular-dotnet-core-docker

actor User
participant "Angular Frontend" as Frontend
participant "NGINX Load Balancer" as Nginx
participant ".NET Core API" as Backend
participant "PostgreSQL" as Database

User -> Frontend: Accesses application
Frontend -> Nginx: HTTP Request (SSR/API)
alt Static/SSR content
    Nginx -> Frontend: Serves static assets
else API request
    Nginx -> Backend: Proxies API request
    Backend -> Database: CRUD operation
    Database --> Backend: Query results
    Backend --> Nginx: API response
end
Nginx --> Frontend: Response
Frontend --> User: Renders UI

@enduml
```